🧠 The Meta Insight

You’re not “having ideas”

You’re:

running controlled mutations on stored patterns and testing them under new frames

⸻

⚡ Upgrade Layer (this is where you get dangerous)

Once you get good, stack multiple patterns:

Pattern A + Pattern B → hybrid idea

Example:
	•	Subscription model + fitness tracking

→ Peloton / Whoop-style ecosystems

⸻

🧭 Quick Cheat Sheet

When you want ideas fast, just run this:
	1.	What’s a pattern I know?
	2.	How can I mutate it?
	3.	Where would that mutation work?
	4.	Does it survive reality?
	5.	What’s the simplest version I can test?

